comment.body:
and also you can see, that gamma doesn't decrease too much if vol goes down, on march 9;
so the zomma effect concentrates to the vol up/gamma up moves, that generates an effect that i call "synthetic circuit breaker", bcs if puts catch bid, momentum is accelerating, downside gamma increases and brakes the momentum swallows volatility.
bcs gamma directly effects realized volatility

